      "role": "user",
      "content": "but it doesnt feel like it's gonna change. everything just feels so heavy and hopeless me and my family are already fighting all the time and school is just a nightmare. like what's even the point of trying to fix something that's already broken? it feels like i'm just stuck in this loop of being hated and i cant see any other way to make it stop.",
